Package: spectrum-knx
Version: @VERSION@
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Depends: python3 (>= 3.13), adduser
Maintainer: Martin Hoefling <martinhoefling@users.noreply.github.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/martinhoefling/SpectrumKNX
Description: Professional KNX bus monitor and analyzer
 Spectrum KNX records and visualizes KNX bus telegrams: live monitor,
 history search, traffic statistics and mixed visualizations, with group
 address names resolved from an uploaded ETS project file.
 .
 This package runs the analyzer as a systemd service with a local SQLite
 database (no PostgreSQL required). It bundles a Python virtual
 environment under /opt/spectrum-knx.
